[13:45] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that have this kind of quizzing adversarial kind of approach to things. So, the next thing that we\'re going to do because we have this like idea that\'s been hashed out. Um they store this, by the way, in your project. So, we\'re in docs, ideas, recipe forking. Now, I\'m'

[13:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'going to run their specter of in development skill. And so, this is going to allow us to actually detail like, well, what does this mean realistically? Like what are the things a user needs to be able to do?'

[14:11] [scene:talk]
