[14:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'structured, and then it will go and build a spec or a PRD for us. So, what we get out the other side of this is, like I said, a PRD. So, what\'s the objective of what we\'re about to try to build? What does success look like? What'

[14:36] [scene:talk]
