AUDIO: 'does it always need to do? What does it need to ask us before it does? What should it never do? Like bypassing row security policies. So, we\'re getting like this detailed version of what needs to be done, but this isn\'t enough to'

[15:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'build from. Like you wouldn\'t want to take this and say, and now go build the thing, right? Because we want to create again vertical slices that we can implement where we have very like verifiable testable stuff. And if we'

[15:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'were to just send this off, like we\'re not necessarily going to get that. And so, the next step of this process then is that we need to first clear out our context. And now what we\'re going to do is we\'re going to do the planning stage.'

